title: The Air Force is Setting Up Tests to Find the Better of Two Fighter Jets
text:
31 The Air Force is Setting Up Tests to Find the Better of Two Fighter Jets 
Government Executive: If you’re the Pentagon, how do you choose between an aging, but dependable, fighter jet and a brand new aircraft that you’re not quite sure is up to the job? You have them fight it out, naturally.
